002package io.vrap.rmf.base.client.error;
003
004import io.vrap.rmf.base.client.ApiHttpHeaders;
005import io.vrap.rmf.base.client.ApiHttpRequest;
006import io.vrap.rmf.base.client.ApiHttpResponse;
007import io.vrap.rmf.base.client.ResponseSerializer;
008
009public class BadGatewayException extends ApiServerException {
010    public BadGatewayException(final int statusCode, final String body, final ApiHttpHeaders headers,
011            final String message, final ApiHttpResponse<byte[]> response) {
012        super(statusCode, body, headers, message, response);
013    }
014
015    public BadGatewayException(final int statusCode, final String body, final ApiHttpHeaders headers,
016            final String message, final ApiHttpResponse<byte[]> response, final ApiHttpRequest request) {
017        super(statusCode, body, headers, message, response, request);
018    }
019
020    public BadGatewayException(final int statusCode, final String body, final ApiHttpHeaders headers,
021            final String message, final ApiHttpResponse<byte[]> response, final ResponseSerializer serializer) {
022        super(statusCode, body, headers, message, response, serializer);
023    }
024
025    public BadGatewayException(final int statusCode, final String body, final ApiHttpHeaders headers,
026            final String message, final ApiHttpResponse<byte[]> response, final ApiHttpRequest request,
027            final ResponseSerializer serializer) {
028        super(statusCode, body, headers, message, response, request, serializer);
029    }
030}
